    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个监控系统的数据流图。核心是从App出发，Metrics收集数据，最后汇总到Dashboard展示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "App",
        "Metrics",
        "Dashboard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，主干是App→Metrics→Dashboard。那Metrics具体从哪些来源采集数据？需要细化吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Metrics"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要四个数据源。首先是HTTP API的请求日志，然后是异常处理的错误日志，还有MySQL的慢查询监控，这三个都汇总到性能指标里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP API calls",
        "Exception handling",
        "MySQL slow queries",
        "Response time, throughput"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：HTTP日志、错误日志、慢查询这三个并行采集，都流向性能指标节点，然后性能指标再到Dashboard？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HTTP API calls",
        "Exception handling",
        "MySQL slow queries",
        "Response time, throughput",
        "Dashboard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Dashboard之前我漏了一个环节。错误日志和性能指标都应该触发告警，Email和SMS通知要单独作为一个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Exception handling",
        "Response time, throughput",
        "Email/SMS notifications"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "收到，那告警节点是双输入？错误日志直接触发告警，性能指标也触发告警，然后Dashboard只接收性能指标的数据？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Exception handling",
        "Response time, throughput",
        "Email/SMS notifications",
        "Dashboard"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
