      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。Dashboard只展示性能指标，比如响应时间和吞吐量。但异常和性能超标都要走告警通道。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dashboard",
        "Response time, throughput",
